{"tid":2187664,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"真名潛水多日，渣狗化名渣B繼續屌網民","createTime":"2020-09-03T19:02:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T11:51:13.000Z","uid":32051,"like":66,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"94719cdf78f888ebc828ff4a467dcf85e3896172","tid":2187664,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T19:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/25xZ5rz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F25xZ5rz.png&h=ad853f3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\">100毛你大股東黎架麻，你想渣狗幾時唔洗再扮渣b咪幾時囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n互含互動依d咁廉價tactic，我請個小學生都識啦，100毛班人真係越玩越廢。<br />\n你地唔撚係以為渣狗咁既過街老狗，試下水溫就無人屌下話。<span class=\"gold\"><br />\n我支持渣狗出真名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n一於互屌，你如果有道理既，驚閪呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"blue\">勇敢面對群眾啦，縮左入老母個墳頭做乜鳩呀？<br />\nBlock人又咁撚勇，俾人屌就縮頭烏龜，正廢柴。</span><br />\n<br />\n另外呀fans Mabel。<br />\n你無為意，好正常，因為渣b打字講嘢個tone同渣狗一撚樣架。<br />\n可能渣b只係一個識打字既人，翻譯返渣狗既吠叫聲，咁樣就當佢地無呃你，當做轉左人管理個page。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n化左名就唔係渣狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8rpxFZ3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8rpxFZ3.png&h=7535f558&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n渣狗，屌你老母咩。<br />\n<span class=\"red\">你條雞蟲搞鳩人果陣，你有無諗過收手呀</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分化你哋？<br />\n你作為「黃圈」既分化先鋒，你地依家內部玩緊統戰呀？<br />\n果然，渣狗係喜歡玩老毛果一套。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJ1j5rO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJ1j5rO.png&h=a43a1b6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />渣狗扮慘俾人直接踢爆<br />\n但依家風頭火勢，又無得block人。<br />\n渣狗眼淚在心裡流<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n駁唔到，點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nv0tekh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnv0tekh.png&h=c550b900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"gold\">渣狗：哼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔驚。我有屈毛大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n死廢老，借d意屈人做龍門打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你會唔會太明顯呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母，你搞鳩人，單打果陣有咩真憑實據呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你搞鳩人，就要人地俾證據解釋。<br />\n依家屌鳩你，你就叫人俾證據先屌你。<br />\n你同證據係咪絕緣架？<br />\n永遠有你講，無人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n龍門任擺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7yFPTL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7yFPTL.png&h=1f240e81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你老母臭閪。<br />\n又單打屈人係打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話你隻渣b背後唔係渣狗都無人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講嘢永遠無point，得返老屈依招。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實你大渣哥真係唔算藍店。<br />\n藍店都無話做大半年怨婦去攻擊其他黃店。<br />\n<strong><br />\n<span class=\"blue\">所以你係賤撚過藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你政治立場係黃，但行為上你比藍店更低賤，你渣狗同藍屍畜牲一樣咁仆街。</strong></span><br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><br />\n咪撚成日搵班傻閪打手spin攻擊你係分化啦，根本無人會之後攻擊其他黃店。<br />\n<br />\n從來網民屌既，只有你渣家軍一眾人渣垃圾。<br />\n唔好講到乜野分化，無差別攻擊黃圈啦，制造恐慌，再打算烏賊戰術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本其他黃店好地地，做好自己，我哋就去幫襯。<br />\n黃圈就係咁簡單。<br />\n人哋唔似你渣狗去分化，網民只會去佢地度幫襯。<br />\n<br />\n咪撚再講到屌鳩你渣家軍，就係攻擊黃圈啦。<br />\n你班狗唔撚配呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VMLQsFy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVMLQsFy.png&h=82fbfb00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n扮乜撚嘢員工呀？<br />\n屌你老母，同舟人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n句嘢都俾你搞到極臭，講出嚟，真係好撚嘔心。<br />\n<br />\n你條撚樣渣狗，又忍唔撚到口，想搵位入龍門。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人哋捐俾龍門就係信佢。<br />\n佢做唔好，自然會有人監察佢<br />\n<br />\n你浸酸味滲晒出嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你賺個圈咁撚多錢，唔係以為食你d嘢好味嗎？<br />\n捐錢拎光環都係marketing遮。<br />\n<br />\n字裡行間都不斷想攻擊龍門，唔撚話你係狗都唔撚得。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n渣狗你癌上腦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uMbzUkJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuMbzUkJ.png&h=5dfce48b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來你條柒頭皮好撚葡萄龍門俾人話佢唔出聲，默默做實事依點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你老母閪，網民讚龍門，再屌鳩你，點解你條柒頭會覺得要計龍門數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點撚樣包括我地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係我睇唔過眼你生癌賤種渣狗，我屌鳩你，又關龍門事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解你條柒頭成日想乘機話人龍門打手呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你既人，無一萬都有幾千，又幾千個打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那依家都出唔撚到幾千個打手搞鳩人啦，你唔係以為龍門有能力搵到幾千人屌